<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>🌾 팜 RPG - 로그인</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="login-bg">
  <div class="login-box">
    <h1>🌱 내 농장에 오신 걸 환영해요!</h1>
    <form action="/login" method="POST">
      <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="농부 이름" required>
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호" required>
      <button type="submit">🚜 로그인</button>
    </form>
    <p>처음이신가요? <a href="/register">회원가입하기</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
